  "text": "In addition, [CITATION_1] stressed on the importance of using technology such as online business and internet as tools in CRM. They proved their point of view by conducting a study on 42 different e-CRM features used by retailers. They found that there is a link between using the features of CRM in retailers' websites and the satisfaction of the customers.",
